'''''Yaaba''''' ni filime y’ikinamico ya [[Burukina Faso|Burkinabé yo mu]] 1989 yanditswe, yakozwe, kandi iyobowe na Idrissa Ouedraogo, "imwe muri filime zizwi cyane zo muri Afurika yo munsi y’ubutayu bwa Sahara"<ref>http://www.ghafla.com/music/don-elvi-yaaba-ft-yaw-tog-kweku-flick/</ref><ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/en/shop/DVD/Yaaba</ref>.  Yatsindiye igihembo cya Sakura Gold mu iserukiramuco rya Filime rya Tokyo mu 1989<ref>https://www.capuseen.com/films/1508-yaaba</ref>.  Iyi filime yatoranijwe muri Burkinabé muri Filime Nziza Y’ururimi rw’amahanga mu bihembo bya 62 bya Academy, ariko ntiyemerwa nk'umukandida. <ref>https://www.trigon-film.org/en/movies/Yaaba</ref> Iyi filime ''yavuzweho na documentaire ngufi Parlons Grand-mère'', yafashwe igihe yatunganyirizwaga na Djibril Diop Mambéty<ref>https://www.cinefil.com/film/yaaba</ref> .

== Umugambi ==
Mu mudugudu wa Mossi [[Burukina Faso|muri Burkinafaso]], Bila (Noufou Ouédraogo), umuhungu w'imyaka icumi, agirana ubucuti n'umukecuru witwa Sana (Fatimata Sanga), washinjwaga kuroga n'umudugudu we. Gusa Bila ''aramwubaha'', akamwita yaaba (Nyirakuru)<ref>https://africanfilmny.org/films/yaaba/</ref>.

Igihe mubyara wa Bila, Nopoko (Roukietou Barry), arwaye, umugabo w’umuganga ashimangira ko Sana yibye roho y’umukobwa. Sana akora urugendo rurerure kandi rutoroshye ariko amaherezo aratsinda kugirango abone imiti irokora ubuzima bwa Nopoko, ariko aracyafatwa nk'umurozi<ref>https://www.quinzaine-realisateurs.com/en/film/yaaba/</ref>.Sana amaze gupfa, impamvu nyayo ituma yangwa mu mudugudu iragaragara, ariko urukundo n'ubwenge yashoye muri Bila na Nopoko birakomeza<ref>https://www.cinefil.com/film/yaaba</ref>.

